# Contributors

This file is part of a **read-only public mirror**. All commits
originate upstream in the private source repository. Contributions
are not accepted in this mirror — see the upstream repo for the
contribution process.

This is a **static informational file**, shipped to the mirror by
`git-filter-repo` like any other allowlisted path. It deliberately
does not embed a frozen contributor list: that data is reproducible
from the repository's own history and would go stale on every commit.
It is no longer synthesized as a commit on top of filter-repo's output.

To list contributors from the current history, run:

    git shortlog -sne

On the mirror, emails appear in the `<localpart>@__GH_REPO__.local`
form (the source identities are rewritten during filtering).
